summary: A student laboratory focusing on Multimedia and Apps, Game Technology and Networking. This lab is semi-managed by the student, from the student, for the student.

EVOLTY is an annual event from Electric Engineering Faculy. Consisting of ELECTRA, a national logics, programming and physics olympiad for Senior High Student, BARONAS, an international robotics championship, and MAGE, a national competition for Senior High Student.

MAGE is an annual event from Computer Engineering degree at Sepuluh Nopember Institute of Technology. It is a part of a bigger annual event that goes by the name of EVOLTY held by Electric Engineering Faculty from the same university. MAGE is consists of National Olympiad, Development Competition and E-Sports Competition.
